race.comment: SEE YA LATER BABY (4) was denied by the barest margin when resuming at Balaklava. Sure to have tightened up from that run and with a strong second-up record, he can go one better. SAN LUCIDO (2) has found consistency again in his last two and looks ready to peak over a favoured trip. The claim helps and he shapes as a genuine threat. SPIRIT OF FLIGHT (12) was doing her best work late when resuming in town. The rise in trip suits and she draws well again for Crowther. Must be taken seriously. PRICILLA'S CHOICE (6) edged out SEE YA LATER BABY two back before a midfield effort in town. A distance specialist who will get back from the draw but can be dangerous late. PRESS EXPRESS (9) doesn't win often but is honest and rarely far away. Draws well for Toeroek and is worth keeping safe.
